{"tid":806794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"福島居民被迫遷離　柴犬守在家7年等主人","createTime":"2018-09-05T03:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T12:29:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":374,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"52b95044d00e495b5178f307440b8dfd185300af","tid":806794,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180821/640_a6febdb14c04833e0da34d9e11c62929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180821%2F640_a6febdb14c04833e0da34d9e11c62929.jpg&h=32e0cbb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">311地震讓許多寵物失去主人。翻攝《天才！志村動物園》</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n距離2011年日本311地震已經發生7年，日本福島因為海嘯的破壞，核電廠的洩漏，對城市造成很嚴重的傷害，不僅奪走人類的家園，更讓許多寵物失去主人，日本節目《天才！志村動物園》攝影團隊近日就前往福島去拍攝，發現一隻柴犬未繫狗繩，仍謹守家門等待主人歸來。<br />\n<br />\n311地震福島核電廠發生一系列事故，導致鄰近地區釋放高劑量輻射，居民被逼離開居住地，日本節目《天才！志村動物園》攝影團隊就到福島飯館村拍攝近況，赫見一隻柴犬自那時開始，一直留守家門，等待主人的回歸，就算是沒有繫上狗繩，也沒有離開家門一步。<br />\n<br />\n當時的災害由於沒有完善的設備，所以臨時避難所是禁止飼養寵物，所以有大量寵物遭受遺留，就寵物狗而言就已經接近200隻；且因為長時間沒有接觸人群，所以對於陌生人有很大的戒備，當主持人想要撫摸時，柴犬就露出凶惡的表情拒絕接觸。<br />\n<br />\n此外，當地的小狗長時間的獨自生活，大型狗的毛髮更是難以整理，這次節目主持人就為此而親自上陣，幫助小狗洗澡，整理毛髮，讓牠在炎熱的夏日，也能夠清爽地生活。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180821/640_0e4c258406991108431d291fb2f8365a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180821%2F640_0e4c258406991108431d291fb2f8365a.jpg&h=9e388729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這隻柴犬未繫狗繩，仍謹守家門等待主人歸來。翻攝《天才！志村動物園》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180821/640_9eb6ce8e2d8ca04af15bda87c6b9487c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180821%2F640_9eb6ce8e2d8ca04af15bda87c6b9487c.jpg&h=376e5a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長時間未接觸人群，對陌生人有很大的戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180821/640_d63b18eac18cccc005cd1473e2e7dc24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180821%2F640_d63b18eac18cccc005cd1473e2e7dc24.jpg&h=8e73a03d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當主持人餵食牠並無異狀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180821/640_78c45103102d67aee89eaedfb45dc47f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180821%2F640_78c45103102d67aee89eaedfb45dc47f.jpg&h=8cce3fd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大型狗的毛髮更是難以整理。翻攝《天才！志村動物園》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180821/640_65079c11910a5589fcda68aadc9b2ee2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180821%2F640_65079c11910a5589fcda68aadc9b2ee2.jpg&h=7f266898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主持人就為親自幫小狗洗澡，整理毛髮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180821/640_beda95f8a1fd95db07ad3273a461b7f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180821%2F640_beda95f8a1fd95db07ad3273a461b7f7.jpg&h=3831961c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓牠在炎熱的夏日，也能夠清爽地生活。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180821/640_1927bafd46bbc81a2ed741d794cea167.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180821%2F640_1927bafd46bbc81a2ed741d794cea167.jpg&h=406c7c19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被迫與主人分離的寵物狗接近200隻。翻攝《天才！志村動物園》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/la/realtime/20180821/1415232/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fla%2Frealtime%2F20180821%2F1415232%2F&d=475R2aNBn2CFmojb1lVuscn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9b7a8cdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fla%2Frealtime%2F20180821%2F1415232%2F&h=2f7c5a9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/la/realtime/20180821/1415232/</a>"},{"pid":"1201c668f8d0bd8fd78d04b805d6e4cbc0a3520e","tid":806794,"uid":191926,"like":793,"dislike":3,"score":790,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7年接近狗的一世<br />\n<br />\n到死都唔知 發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8c78443c20ba2afd6d132c08fa10491b4e0212","tid":806794,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":154,"score":-145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"好慘呀班狗狗 點解之後主人唔接番佢地"},{"pid":"d7455bbb689239c4d7ef513d364c830b4b0bd776","tid":806794,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:53:12.000Z","msg":"狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36629771bbdcc5101c4eac8f929e3a2633ec4caf","tid":806794,"uid":115270,"like":196,"dislike":2,"score":194,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"喺你後面啊！！！"},{"pid":"670ca32f6fc7d5e900c2111833fcbc6bfbd8a82f","tid":806794,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"會唔會異變"},{"pid":"3851be88c1e8a7c696d09d63fa22f7e57cce9dc7","tid":806794,"uid":176472,"like":529,"dislike":4,"score":525,"quote":{"pid":"2b8c78443c20ba2afd6d132c08fa10491b4e0212","tid":806794,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":154,"score":-145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"好慘呀班狗狗 點解之後主人唔接番佢地"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"因為 佢地已經死左了&hellip;"},{"pid":"7b04f66030a12c5854053580bf73c989c98afcab","tid":806794,"uid":11694,"like":257,"dislike":2,"score":255,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:56:28.000Z","msg":"佢地靠咩食到七年咁耐"},{"pid":"0003624745e25ee818905cd914a372be580aa1e4","tid":806794,"uid":8949,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"東京jungle"},{"pid":"ddbe9d8daf6b8d