東日本大震災牽連甚廣，造成極大破壞令各區<span style=\"color: red;\">沒餘力再為寵物們提供救助</span>，加上臨時住所不能飼養寵物，令主人們被逼拋下心愛的毛孩們撤離災區，飯館村當時已有近200隻狗被留下。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">幸得義工團體的幫助，飯館村的毛孩們仍能存活至今</span>。當中有一隻柴犬每天都待在門前，寸步不離地守候著，深信主人有一天會回來...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就似平日一邊人道毀滅流浪貓狗，一邊就繼續喂佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cfe56fca2f1b08f8292daa515c3ac2f122d6d1","tid":806794,"uid":11097,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f219646db104ab3efcca903422cfbca42f362ad7","tid":806794,"uid":51701,"like":399,"dislike":6,"score":393,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"見到日本狗狗咁慘, 好傷心<br />\n見到支那人成個省死左都唔會傷心<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母我係咪痴左線?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"你冇呀，絕對正常<br />\n我願意用支那滅國去換返福島所有寵物動物既生命"},{"pid":"80ef1d255d76b8803b345d58108596831822e50c","tid":806794,"uid":166637,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/151419_6f44a4af0017fff48ff1151176a2e687.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F151419_6f44a4af0017fff48ff1151176a2e687.png&h=ba512bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好心人餵 餵到自己都受幅射影響<br />\n<br />\n仲有攝影師幫手:<br />\n<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/130018/一直餵飼、拍攝、幫助「福島飯館村遺棄貓狗」的/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F130018%2F%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A4%B5%E9%A3%BC%E3%80%81%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E3%80%81%E5%B9%AB%E5%8A%A9%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%8F%E5%B3%B6%E9%A3%AF%E9%A4%A8%E6%9D%91%E9%81%BA%E6%A3%84%E8%B2%93%E7%8B%97%E3%80%8D%E7%9A%84%2F&d=475R2aNBn2CFmojb1lVuscn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=df5f7547\" target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/130018/一直餵飼、拍攝、幫助「福島飯館村遺棄貓狗」的/</a>"},{"pid":"2a0e1da377dd4313b879c34bc472cfdc18518aac","tid":806794,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cf9a113150e48f4b1d00f92237e8f36235c1baa","tid":806794,"uid":145779,"lik